source.name: EPA Water Services - NWISQWResultService
source.description: The WATERS Web and Database services provide open interfaces to complex analyses. These services make extensive use of the NHD and referenced program data in the RAD, and also integrate other WATERS program data. Designed as loosely coupled modular units, the services are developed in a common architecture.  Retrieves water-quality result data.
